Package base_SOM_Objects.som_examples

Class SOM_MapNode

java.lang.Object
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.base.baseDataPtVis
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.SOM_Example
base_SOM_Objects.som_examples.SOM_MapNode
Direct Known Subclasses:
SOM_GeomMapNode
public abstract class SOM_MapNode extends SOM_Example
objects of inheritors to this abstract class represent nodes in the SOM. The instancing class is responsible for managing any connections to underlying src data, which is project dependent
Author:
john
